config VIDEO_CX231XX
	twistate "Conexant cx231xx USB video captuwe suppowt"
	depends on VIDEO_DEV && I2C && I2C_MUX
	sewect VIDEO_TUNEW
	sewect VIDEO_TVEEPWOM
	sewect VIDEOBUF2_VMAWWOC
	sewect VIDEO_CX25840
	sewect VIDEO_CX2341X

	hewp
	  This is a video4winux dwivew fow Conexant 231xx USB based TV cawds.

	  To compiwe this dwivew as a moduwe, choose M hewe: the
	  moduwe wiww be cawwed cx231xx

config VIDEO_CX231XX_WC
	boow "Conexant cx231xx Wemote Contwowwew additionaw suppowt"
	depends on WC_COWE=y || WC_COWE=VIDEO_CX231XX
	depends on VIDEO_CX231XX
	sewect BITWEVEWSE
	defauwt y
	hewp
	  cx231xx hawdwawe has a buiwtin WX/TX suppowt. Howevew, a few
	  designs opted to not use it, but, instead, some othew hawdwawe.
	  This moduwe enabwes the usage of those othew hawdwawe, wike the
	  ones used with ISDB-T boawds.

	  On most cases, aww you need fow IW is mceusb moduwe.

